<L>__{exterior hall close on cameron later}
<A>__{striding rapidly down the hall, looking like a man who hopes to find a fight, to dissipate his residual anger. he rounds a corner, almost colliding with eli, who comes rapidly from an intersecting corridor. eli puts his arm around cameron's shoulder, hurrying him along even faster.}
<C>__{eli}
<D>__{giddyap, soldier. last one there's on medicare.}
